# PYDownloader

**PYDownloader** is an advanced, lightweight, async file downloader built using Python and `aiohttp`, featuring:

- ğŸ”„ Pause/Resume support  
- ğŸ“¶ Live speed & progress tracking  
- ğŸ“¥ Multi-format download (ZIP, MP4, MP3, etc.)
- ğŸ–¼ï¸ Beautiful dark-themed UI (using `ttkbootstrap`)
- ğŸ® System tray minimization support
- ğŸ”” Sound notification on download completion
- ğŸ§  Smart retry and resume support

